  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t转自推特用户Jackson 贴贴BOT<br/>\n<br/>\r\n《蒋帮统治下的台湾》，出版于1977年<br/>\n<br/>\r\n书的核心主旨是揭露蒋介石统治的黑暗。但讽刺的是，每一条都能在当代中国找到写照。以下是原文内容摘录：<br/>\n<br/>\r\n1. 扉页插图写着：解放台湾！<br/>\r\n2. 台湾经济：技术落后，危机四伏。<br/>\r\n3. 台湾劳工：高强度工作，饱受压榨。上班期间上个厕所都要扣工钱。工资赶不上物价飞涨<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTUwMzVkM2Y1ODI2OTkxNmExZmJjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/15035d3f58269916a1fbc.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/15035d3f58269916a1fbc.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/15035d3f58269916a1fbc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGYwMGNhZDU4NGQxZGIwMWNiZjJiLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0f00cad584d1db01cbf2b.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0f00cad584d1db01cbf2b.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0f00cad584d1db01cbf2b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjJiM2U5ZjU4ZGVlZmYwNGViNjIzLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b2b3e9f58deeff04eb623.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b2b3e9f58deeff04eb623.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b2b3e9f58deeff04eb623.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTJmNmQ0Yjg5MWQ4ZTA0MjYyNzNhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/92f6d4b891d8e0426273a.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/92f6d4b891d8e0426273a.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/92f6d4b891d8e0426273a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n4. 在台湾，创作没有自由。文艺创作只能听党话，灌输效忠思想。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n5. 蒋介石苛捐杂税多，人民叫苦连天。不仅如此，他们还滥印钞票，大发债务。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n6. 在蒋帮统治下的台湾，毕业即失业，许多人争着抢铁饭碗，僧多粥少。这成为了严重的社会问题<br/>\n<br/>\r\n7. 黑暗的统治造成了穷人「生病没有命」，不给钱就不给治。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzk2ZmUwOWRiYTI0MWJlYzM3ZjE1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/796fe09dba241bec37f15.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/796fe09dba241bec37f15.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/796fe09dba241bec37f15.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzAwODNmZTc4MmVlZjdmMzdhMWZjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/70083fe782eef7f37a1fc.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/70083fe782eef7f37a1fc.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/70083fe782eef7f37a1fc.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjJlYzQyZWQwMDBhOTU1MTA0ZmQ5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/62ec42ed000a955104fd9.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/62ec42ed000a955104fd9.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/62ec42ed000a955104fd9.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWY0ZTBjYzZkYmZhYmJiMmI3NGE4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f4e0cc6dbfabbb2b74a8.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f4e0cc6dbfabbb2b74a8.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f4e0cc6dbfabbb2b74a8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n8. 蒋介石统治下，医疗道德败坏，医疗成为了赚钱的工具。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n9. 不少黑心商家制造假食品、假饮料，毒害人民身心健康。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n10. 警察，特务横行，人民群众受到严酷的镇压。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n11. 新闻没有自由，说真话有罪。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMGJlYmQwZGE1ZDRmZmFmYTMxNjFjLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0bebd0da5d4ffafa3161c.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0bebd0da5d4ffafa3161c.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/0bebd0da5d4ffafa3161c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjgwMTg4ODdkMDc1MTQ4ZDZkOWY3LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f8018887d075148d6d9f7.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f8018887d075148d6d9f7.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f8018887d075148d6d9f7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWY2NmU3MmUzMDA1NjBhZGMwYzRlLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1f66e72e300560adc0c4e.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1f66e72e300560adc0c4e.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1f66e72e300560adc0c4e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmVhODE3YTRiZDlkZDg4NDFhZTNiLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bea817a4bd9dd8841ae3b.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bea817a4bd9dd8841ae3b.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bea817a4bd9dd8841ae3b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n12. 蒋介石禁止人民收听敌台、外国报道的新闻。同时，他们对书刊报纸进行严格的审查，一字一句都不放过。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n13.  蒋介石残酷迫害政治犯，实施严刑拷打。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n14. 蒋介石的法律保护官僚特权阶级、保护洋人；对普通民众则宁可错抓，不放一人。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n15. 在蒋介石的黑暗统治下，人民不堪其压，不少人选择看不开。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDAyMTgwMzQxMDg1ZGZkNGI4N2E4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/402180341085dfd4b87a8.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/402180341085dfd4b87a8.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/402180341085dfd4b87a8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2NjMjEwYTc2ZGJiMTc5NzVkNzk0LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7cc210a76dbb17975d794.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7cc210a76dbb17975d794.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7cc210a76dbb17975d794.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGNhYWYyNWQzZDM1ODE0YzZkYjIwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dcaaf25d3d35814c6db20.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dcaaf25d3d35814c6db20.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dcaaf25d3d35814c6db20.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTkxZjI4ODIxNjgxMzQ5NzUyZjViLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/991f28821681349752f5b.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/991f28821681349752f5b.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/991f28821681349752f5b.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
